      "examples": [
        {
          "kp": "Sarad ing pintuan.",
          "en": "The door is closed."
        },
        {
          "kp": "Bukasan me ing pintuan.",
          "en": "Open the door."
        }
      ],
      "notes": "From Spanish 'puerta' + Tagalog/Kapampangan suffix -an (place of). Refers to a door or doorway. Confidence: very high."
    },
    {
