      "theme": "Objects and people you interact with every day",
      "intro": "This lesson covers five words that come up constantly in everyday Kapampangan life. 'Libro' (book) and 'tubig' (water) are basic necessities. 'Susi' (key) unlocks your home and car. 'Kotse' (car) is the common term for any vehicle. And 'tao' (person/people) is one of the most fundamental nouns in any language — you use it whenever you talk about someone.",
      "wordIds": [
        "ev-libro",
        "ev-tubig",
        "ev-susi",
        "ev-kotse",
        "ev-tao"
      ],
      "exercises": [
